ass":130,"line":892},[128,1539,398],{"class":149},[128,1541,1542],{"class":130,"line":907},[128,1543,259],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":258},[128,1545,1546],{"class":130,"line":913},[128,1547,1548],{"class":202},"\u002F\u002F 測試範例\n",[128,1550,1551,1553,1555,1557,1559,1561,1563],{"class":130,"line":919},[128,1552,135],{"class":134},[128,1554,1309],{"class":138},[128,1556,169],{"class":134},[128,1558,1412],{"class":369},[128,1560,679],{"class":149},[128,1562,246],{"class":134},[128,1564,1314],{"class":149},[128,1566,1567,1569,1571,1573,1575,1577,1579,1581,1583],{"class":130,"line":925},[128,1568,1319],{"class":149},[128,1570,431],{"class":138},[128,1572,1324],{"class":149},[128,1574,1327],{"class":145},[128,1576,1330],{"class":149},[128,1578,1333],{"class":138},[128,1580,1336],{"class":149},[128,1582,695],{"class":138},[128,1584,1341],{"class":149},[128,1586,1587,1589,1591,1593,1595,1597,1599,1601,1603],{"class":130,"line":1170},[128,1588,1319],{"class":149},[128,1590,436],{"class":138},[128,1592,1324],{"class":149},[128,1594,1352],{"class":145},[128,1596,1330],{"class":149},[128,1598,1357],{"class":138},[128,1600,1336],{"class":149},[128,1602,436],{"class":138},[128,1604,1341],{"class":149},[128,1606,1607],{"class":130,"line":1183},[128,1608,698],{"class":149},[128,1610,1611],{"class":130,"line":1188},[128,1612,259],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":258},[128,1614,1615,1617,1619,1621,1623,1625],{"class":130,"line":1193},[128,1616,1376],{"class":149},[128,1618,1379],{"class":362},[128,1620,366],{"class":149},[128,1622,1384],{"class":362},[128,1624,1387],{"class":149},[128,1626,1390],{"class":202},[12,1628,1629,1630,1633,1634,1637],{},"轉換的過程中，你的程式碼確實透過 TypeScript 提高了可維護性，但是如果你不小心在重構過程中改變了邏輯，例如將 ",[125,1631,1632],{},"item.price * item.quantity"," 改成了 ",[125,1635,1636],{},"item.price + item.quantity","，這時候如果你沒有撰寫測試的話，你就很難發現這個錯誤，因為 TypeScript 並不會幫你檢查邏輯上的錯誤，所以我個人會建議在專案有寫測試的情況下，才使用 TypeScript。",[12,1639,1640],{},"因為你也很難保證你在轉換過程中，不會不小心粗手指，所以我個人會建議在專案有寫測試的情況下，才引入 TypeScript。",[719,1642,1644],{"id":1643},"團隊成員都有-typescript-基礎","團隊成員都有 TypeScript 基礎",[12,1646,1647],{},"這是一個我認為滿重要的事情，有些 Team Leader（團隊負責人） 看到人家宣傳 TypeScript 有多香之後，就想要將專案轉換成 TypeScript，但是他們忘記了一件事情，就是團隊成員是否都有 TypeScript 基礎，如果團隊成員都沒有 TypeScript 基礎，那麼你就必須要花一些時間來學習 TypeScript。",[12,1649,1650],{},"如果是專案時程不受任何影響的話，那麼我認為還是可以引入 TypeScript，但是如果是專案時程很趕的話，那麼我建議還是不要引入 TypeScript，因為你們必須要花一些時間來學習 TypeScript。",[12,1652,1653],{},"「所以我們就只能放棄 TypeScript 嗎？」",[12,1655,1656],{},"話不是這樣說的，只是我認為在嘗試使用 TypeScript 之前，你們可以嘗試撰寫 JSDoc，JSDoc 是一種註解語法，可以讓你在撰寫 JavaScript 時，可以寫上一些註解，讓你的程式碼更加的清楚，而且也可以讓你的程式碼有一些型別檢查，例如：",[118,1658,1660],{"className":120,"code":1659,"language":122,"meta":123,"style":123},"\u002F**\n * 計算總價\n * @param {number} a\n * @param {number} b\n * @returns {number}\n *\u002F\nfunction add(a, b) {\n  return a + b;\n}\n",[125,1661,1662,1667,1672,1686,1697,1707,1712,1728,1738],{"__ignoreMap":123},[128,1663,1664],{"class":130,"line":131},[128,1665,1666],{"class":202},"\u002F**\n",[128,1668,1669],{"class":130,"line":255},[128,1670,1671],{"class":202}," * 計算總價\n",[128,1673,1674,1677,1680,1683],{"class":130,"line":262},[128,1675,1676],{"class":202}," * ",[128,1678,1679],{"class":134},"@param",[128,1681,1682],{"class":369}," {number}",[128,1684,1685],{"class":149}," a\n",[128,1687,1688,1690,1692,1694],{"class":130,"line":547},[128,1689,1676],{"class":202},[128,1691,1679],{"class":134},[128,1693,1682],{"class":369},[128,1695,1696],{"class":149}," b\n",[128,1698,1699,1701,1704],{"class":130,"line":553},[128,1700,1676],{"class":202},[128,1702,1703],{"class":134},"@returns",[128,1705,1706],{"class":369}," {number}\n",[128,1708,1709],{"class":130,"line":558},[128,1710,1711],{"class":202}," *\u002F\n",[128,1713,1714,1716,1718,1720,1722,1724,1726],{"class":130,"line":569},[128,1715,359],{"class":134},[128,1717,363],{"class":362},[128,1719,366],{"class":149},[128,1721,370],{"class":369},[128,1723,373],{"class":149},[128,1725,376],{"class":369},[128,1727,379],{"class":149},[128,1729,1730,1732,1734,1736],{"class":130,"line":850},[128,1731,384],{"class":134},[128,1733,387],{"class":149},[128,1735,390],{"class":134},[128,1737,393],{"class":149},[128,1739,1740],{"class":130,"line":865},[128,1741,398],{"class":149},[12,1743,1744],{},"習慣撰寫 JSDoc 對於你們未來轉換 TypeScript 會有一些幫助，因為概念上 TypeScript 的型別註記跟 JSDoc 的註解有點類似，這樣子的陣痛期也是相對比較少的，所以我建議在專案時程很趕的情況下，可以先嘗試撰寫 JSDoc，等到專案時程不趕時，再來嘗試轉換 TypeScript。",[1746,1747,1748],"blockquote",{},[12,1749,1750,1753,1754,1760],{},[39,1751,1752],{},"Note","\n這邊我也提供一篇我先前寫的文章「",[370,1755,1759],{"href":1756,"rel":1757},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fjavascript\u002F20230513\u002F284079926\u002F",[1758],"nofollow","沒辦法用 TypeScript？別擔心，你還可以寫 JSDoc 標注類型","」。",[719,1762,1764],{"id":1763},"typescript-並非萬靈藥","TypeScript 並非萬靈藥",[12,1766,1767],{},"有件事情我必須要先跟你說，並不是代表使用 TypeScript 就不會發生 JavaScript 的一些隱含雷點，你必須熟記一個原因",[12,1769,1770],{},"「TypeScript 本質上是 JavaScript 的超集合（SuperSet），因此編譯出來的程式碼還是 JavaScript。」",[12,1772,1773],{},"千萬不要認為使用了 TypeScript 就可以避掉 JavaScript 的一些隱含雷點，例如...你寫了一個表單功能，然後你都有針對這些表單物件寫上型別註記，但實際上編譯出來後，還是 JavaScript，底下是一個簡單的範例：",[118,1775,1777],{"className":156,"code":1776,"language":158,"meta":123,"style":123},"type Form = {\n  name: string;\n  email: string;\n  phone: string;\n};\n\nconst form: Form = {\n  name: '',\n  email: '',\n  phone: '',\n};\n",[125,1778,1779,1790,1800,1811,1822,1826,1830,1845,1856,1865,1874],{"__ignoreMap":123},[128,1780,1781,1783,1786,1788],{"class":130,"line":131},[128,1782,941],{"class":134},[128,1784,1785],{"class":369}," Form",[128,1787,142],{"class":134},[128,1789,614],{"class":149},[128,1791,1792,1794,1796,1798],{"class":130,"line":255},[128,1793,1432],{"class":369},[128,1795,169],{"class":134},[128,1797,172],{"class":138},[128,1799,150],{"class":149},[128,1801,1802,1805,1807,1809],{"class":130,"line":262},[128,1803,1804],{"class":369},"  email",[128,1806,169],{"class":134},[128,1808,172],{"class":138},[128,1810,150],{"class":149},[128,1812,1813,1816,1818,1820],{"class":130,"line":547},[128,1814,1815],{"class":369},"  phone",[128,1817,169],{"class":134},[128,1819,172],{"class":138},[128,1821,150],{"class":149},[128,1823,1824],{"class":130,"line":553},[128,1825,928],{"class":149},[128,1827,1828],{"class":130,"line":558},[128,1829,259],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":258},[128,1831,1832,1834,1837,1839,1841,1843],{"class":130,"line":569},[128,1833,135],{"class":134},[128,1835,1836],{"class":138}," form",[128,1838,169],{"class":134},[128,1840,1785],{"class":369},[128,1842,142],{"class":134},[128,1844,614],{"class":149},[128,1846,1847,1850,1853],{"class":130,"line":850},[128,1848,1849],{"class":149},"  name: ",[128,1851,1852],{"class":145},"''",[128,1854,1855],{"class":149},",\n",[128,1857,1858,1861,1863],{"class":130,"line":865},[128,1859,1860],{"class":149},"  email: ",[128,1862,1852],{"class":145},[128,1864,1855],{"class":149},[128,1866,1867,1870,1872],{"class":130,"line":877},[128,1868,1869],{"class":149},"  phone: ",[128,1871,1852],{"class":145},[128,1873,1855],{"class":149},[128,1875,1876],{"class":130,"line":886},[128,1877,928],{"class":149},[12,1879,1880],{},"實際上編譯出來還是 JavaScript，如下：",[118,1882,1884],{"className":120,"code":1883,"language":122,"meta":123,"style":123},"\"use strict\";\nconst form = {\n    name: '',\n    email: '',\n    phone: '',\n};\n",[125,1885,1886,1893,1903,1912,1921,1930],{"__ignoreMap":123},[128,1887,1888,1891],{"class":130,"line":131},[128,1889,1890],{"class":145},"\"use strict\"",[128,1892,150],{"class":149},[128,1894,1895,1897,1899,1901],{"class":130,"line":255},[128,1896,135],{"class":134},[128,1898,1836],{"class":138},[128,1900,142],{"class":134},[128,1902,614],{"class":149},[128,1904,1905,1908,1910],{"class":130,"line":262},[128,1906,1907],{"class":149},"    name: ",[128,1909,1852],{"class":145},[128,1911,1855],{"class":149},[128,1913,1914,1917,1919],{"class":130,"line":547},[128,1915,1916],{"class":149},"    email: ",[128,1918,1852],{"class":145},[128,1920,1855],{"class":149},[128,1922,1923,1926,1928],{"class":130,"line":553},[128,1924,1925],{"class":149},"    phone: ",[128,1927,1852],{"class":145},[128,1929,1855],{"class":149},[128,1931,1932],{"class":130,"line":558},[128,1933,928],{"class":149},[1935,1936],"code-pen",{"default-tab":1937,"height":1938,"slug":1939,"title":1940,"user":1941},"result",300,"qBgzRzM","typescript-example","hsiangfeng",[12,1943,1944],{},"因此你本身的 JavaScript 程式碼邏輯還是有可能出現一些隱含雷點，該做的預防你還是閃不掉，千萬不要認為使用了 TypeScript 就解決了所有問題，因為 TypeScript 本質上還是 JavaScript。",[719,1946,1948],{"id":1947},"typescript-共同規範","TypeScript 共同規範",[12,1950,1951,1952,1955,1956,1958],{},"不得不說 TypeScript 的型別機制確實讓我們減少了許多開發雷點，也提升了開發體驗（Developer Experience，又稱 DX），我曾經看過有開發者用著 TypeScript 卻全部都使用 ",[125,1953,1954],{},"any"," 來作為註記，但是難道我們就完全不能使用 ",[125,1957,1954],{}," 嗎？",[12,1960,1961,1962,1964,1965,1967,1968,1970],{},"不對，而是要依據你的需求來決定是否使用 ",[125,1963,1954],{},"，如果你能夠知道該變數的型別，那麼就不要使用 ",[125,1966,1954],{},"，但是如果你無法知道該變數的型別，那麼你就可以使用 ",[125,1969,1954],{},"。",[12,1972,1973,1974,1976],{},"例如...你有一個函式，但是你不知道該函式的回傳值型別，這時候你就可以使用 ",[125,1975,1954],{},"，如下：",[118,1978,1980],{"className":156,"code":1979,"language":158,"meta":123,"style":123},"function getSomething(): any {\n  \u002F\u002F ...\n}\n",[125,1981,1982,1999,2004],{"__ignoreMap":123},[128,1983,1984,1986,1989,1992,1994,1997],{"class":130,"line":131},[128,1985,359],{"class":134},[128,1987,1988],{"class":362}," getSomething",[128,1990,1991],{"class":149},"()",[128,1993,169],{"class":134},[128,1995,1996],{"class":138}," any",[128,1998,614],{"class":149},[128,2000,2001],{"class":130,"line":255},[128,2002,2003],{"class":202},"  \u002F\u002F ...\n",[128,2005,2006],{"class":130,"line":262},[128,2007,398],{"class":149},[12,2009,2010,2011,2013,2014,2016,2017,1970],{},"但把握一個原則，就是盡量不要使用 ",[125,2012,1954],{},"，因為你使用 ",[125,2015,1954],{}," 就代表你放棄了 TypeScript 的型別檢查，所以盡量不要使用 ",[125,2018,1954],{},[12,2020,2021],{},[2022,2023,2024,2025],"del",{},"要這樣子寫不如就改叫 ",[125,2026,2027],{},"AnyScript",[19,2029,2030],{"id":2030},"結論",[12,2032,2033],{},"以上差不多就是我自己對於 TypeScript 以及為什麼要用的看法了，希望可以讓初次接觸 TypeScript 的開發者，可以對 TypeScript 有一些初步的認識，以及為什麼要用 TypeScript，而非盲目跟風的導入。",[2035,2036,2037],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}",{"title":123,"searchDepth":255,"depth":255,"links":2039},[2040,2041,2042,2043,2050],{"id":21,"depth":255,"text":21},{"id":27,"depth":255,"text":28},{"id":109,"depth":255,"text":110},{"id":713,"depth":255,"text":714,"children":2044},[2045,2046,2047,2048,2049],{"id":721,"depth":262,"text":722},{"id":1206,"depth":262,"text":1206},{"id":1643,"depth":262,"text":1644},{"id":1763,"depth":262,"text":1764},{"id":1947,"depth":262,"text":1948},{"id":2030,"depth":255,"text":2030},"TypeScript","2023-12-15 10:17:49","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Ftypescript\u002Ftypescript","9",{"title":6,"description":24},false,"TypeScript\u002F閒聊-TypeScript-這個東西與為什麼用",[2051,2062],"JavaScript",null,"\u002FTypeScript\u002F20231215\u002F812573601\u002F","L_SquWwoqn60fuDJzrnTsePEwSwsE-qZNCl3c44qd08",{"newer":2067,"older":2071},{"url":2068,"title":2069,"date":2070},"\u002Fother\u002F20231224\u002F4103794407\u002F","Windows 自然人憑證網頁總是出現「localhost 拒絕連線」的解決方式","2023-12-24 0